Delta 209	Dulles Approach Control
air traffic communication
Delta 209 communicated with Dulles Approach Control on frequency 134.2.

ATC Controller	Delta 209
air traffic control interaction
Delta 209 communicated with the ATC Controller for handoff communication.

Dulles Airport	Dulles Approach Control
air traffic management
Dulles Approach Control is responsible for air traffic control at Dulles Airport.

Aerostar 2699G	Aerostar 99G
aircraft communication, flight instructions
Aerostar 2699G is being instructed to contact Washington at frequency 3000, while Aerostar 99G is being instructed to fly heading 330 and climb to 4000 feet.

ATC Controller	Aerostar 99G
guidance, instruction
"The ATC Controller is guiding the Aerostar 99G pilot through instructions.

Aerostar 99G	Altitude and Heading Adjustment Instruction
pilot guidance, event participation
"The Aerostar 99G is receiving the Altitude and Heading Adjustment Instruction from the ATC Controller.

Climb and maintain 4000 feet	Fly heading 330
instruction component, altitude maneuver
"Fly heading 330 is a part of the Climb and maintain 4000 feet instruction.

ATC	Aero Star 99G
aircraft and controller interaction, communication
Aero Star 99G communicates with ATC for flight instructions, such as climb instructions and altitude changes.

Aero Star 99G	Washington Departure Controller
controller guidance, aircraft action
Washington Departure Controller issues climb instructions to Aero Star 99G, guiding it to adjust altitude.

Aero Star 99G	Climb Instruction
aircraft action, instruction execution
Aero Star 99G executes climb instructions, adjusting its altitude as instructed by ATC.

Altitude Change Report	Washington Departure Controller
controller monitoring, aircraft reporting
Washington Departure Controller receives altitude change reports from Aero Star 99G, monitoring its flight status.

Aerostar 99G	Casanova
aircraft-air traffic controller interaction
Aerostar 99G is communicating with Casanova for navigation instructions and frequency change.

Aerostar 99G	Dulles Approach
aircraft-airport interaction
Aerostar 99G is communicating with Dulles Approach for navigation instructions and frequency change.

Casanova	Washington Center
air traffic controller-air traffic control center interaction
Casanova communicates with Washington Center for navigation and frequency changes.

USAir 237	Washington Departure Radar Contact
air traffic control, aircraft instruction<SEP>air traffic control, communication establishment
USAir 237 made contact with Washington Departure Radar Contact to establish communication and altitude instructions.<SEP>Washington Departure Radar Contact gave instructions to USAir 237 to establish radar contact and maintain 5,000 feet.

Climb to 5,000 Feet	USAir 237
altitude instruction, aircraft response
USAir 237 was instructed to climb to 5,000 feet by Washington Departure Radar Contact.
